dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows provincial, district, planning area, municipal or township, property and cadastral boundaries. Includes index to sheets. "(N. A. 36, V. II. 21¹)." "Surveyed (October 1960) and drawn (February 1961) by Lands & Surveys Department, Uganda." "Crown copyright reserved." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of the existence of a right of way." "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." "200-5-61."
dc_creator_sm: Uganda. Department of Lands and Surveys
